Package: birdcage
Title: An App for Interactive Analysis, Transformation, and I/O of Twitter Data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Brendan", "Knapp", 
           email = "brendan.g.knapp@nps.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3284-4972"))
Description: 
    `{birdcage}` is an app enabling interactive temporal, spatial, and network analysis in 
    addition to multi-source I/O and data transformation operations.
